	"

9392, "(fr)Commissioned during the Second Shivan Incursion, the Morning Star is a tactical weapon designed to disrupt and degrade enemy bomber formations. With superb range and velocity and a shockwave effect on jacket collapse, the Morningstar excels at warhead intercept.
"

